  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Comparative Analysis of Tourism Regulatory Framework in Post Conflict Countries</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">International Alert proposes to identify global lessons learnt in the promotion of tourism in post-conflict settings and recommend good practice for the Government of Punjab. The output of the assignment will be a concise report (maximum 20 pages) including case studies from eight post-conflict/conflict-affected situations, outlining in each case the: Conflict context/history; Pre-conflict tourism situation; Post-conflict security and tourism situations; Key policy/regulatory steps taken to improve tourism</narrative>
  </description>
